# ── Claude Code agent state ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Transient worktrees + agent bookkeeping created by Claude Code while
# it runs in the repo. Never useful in commits; gitignored at the
# directory level so a stray gitlink to a temporary worktree branch
# can't sneak back into history.
.claude/

# ── Internal planning / agent docs ─────────────────────────────────────
# These are working documents for the Architect/Builder/Reviewer agent
# pipeline. They guide development but are not part of the public app
# distribution. Keep them local; the public repo is just the app + release
# infrastructure (build-dmg.sh, release-github.sh, appcast.xml stay tracked).
BRIEF.md
SPEC.md
DECISIONS.md
QUESTIONS.md
BUILD_LOG.md
REVIEW.md
architect.md
builder.md
reviewer.md

# ── Sparkle EdDSA private key ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated by Sparkle's `bin/generate_keys`. Public key lives in
# build-dmg.sh (and the resulting Info.plist). Loss = need new keypair +
# version-bumped public key + manual reinstall for existing users.
keyfile.txt

# ── Release pipeline handoff files ─────────────────────────────────────
.release-metadata
.release-notes-draft.md
RELEASE_NOTES.md
Manifold-*.dmg

